originalText.text: A Realtor by the name of Gabrielle Nabatian set up my viewing to see an Apartment, got the Application even kept in contact a couple hours prior. We was suppose to meet a 5:30 she sends me the number to the Super, I called 3 times no answer. I Called her # no answer so I text and all she says is please wait I ask for a time frame I've been there about 15mins or more at that point I wait longer and text her I'm leaving and she never replied apologized or anything.  That's when I texted her and let her know she's Ghetto and I've never seen a Real Estate Agent so Unprofessional in my life. Like I really took a trip to Harlem from Queens for nothing.
